column2: SELECT TOP TEN  a.specObjID, a.plateid, a.mjd,  a.targettype, a.z, a.ra, a.dec, a.spectrotype,  b.lick_hd_a, b.lick_hd_a_err, b.lick_hd_a_model,  b.lick_hd_a_sub, b.lick_hd_a_sub_err,  b.d4#_n, b.d4#_n_err, b.d4#_n_model,  b.d4#_n_sub, b.d4#_n_sub_err,  c.lgm_tot_p5#, c.sfr_tot_p5# FROM galSpecInfo AS a  JOIN galSpecIndx AS b   ON a.specObjID = b.specObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra AS c   ON a.specObjID = c.specObjID
